I did a "NEW DROP" after a long time
The puppy I had been with for 13 years crossed the rainbow and went on a picnic.
It was difficult, but I think I was comforted by the illustration.

This time, I caught a student attending a magic school as a concept.
As a  naughty girl character, I mixed a clown image and a witch image.

Story >
With a mischievous personality like a Small devil, she is at the center of various incidents, but the Magic School evaluates and monitors her abilities.
This evening, I set off firecrackers during an outdoor class and created a festive atmosphere saying that this is not the atmosphere I wanted.
However, the reason he cannot catch her is that she runs away with her magical and scientific flying abilities.
Will her mischief ever stop before graduation?
